Package: MRTrios
Title: Mendelian Randomization analysis for genomic trios 
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Bandita", "Karki", , "kark6289@vandals.uidaho.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID")), person("Audrey", "Fu", ,
                    "audreyf@uidaho.edu", role = c("aut")))
Maintainer: Audrey Q. Fu <audreyqyfu@gmail.com>
Description: This package forms trios between biological processes like methylation, gene expression, and copy number alteration based on gene names and their Entrez IDs. Then it applies mendelian randomization
             to the trios and infer a genetic regulatory network.
License: `use_gpl3_license()`
Encoding: UTF-8
